[49m[38;5;9m- 125     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m **Amazon SNS for intervention notifications.** When a patient is scored as high-risk, the appropriate care team needs to be notified immediately. SNS delivers notifications to care transition nurses, case managers, or automated workflow systems based on the risk tier and contributing factors.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      125[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Amazon SNS for intervention notifications.** When a patient is scored as high-risk, the appropriate care team needs to be notified immediately. SNS delivers notifications to care transition nurses, case managers, or automated workflow systems based on the risk tier and contributing factors. Important: SNS messages containing patient identifiers and clinical indicators constitute PHI. Restrict topic subscriptions to HIPAA-compliant endpoints only (Lambda functions, SQS queues within your VPC, or HTTPS endpoints covered under your BAA). Do not use email or SMS subscriptions for messages containing patient-level data. If email notification is needed, send a minimal alert ("1 new high-risk discharge requires review") with a link to the secure care management dashboard.
